quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  86,1,By the sky and the Nightcomer
  86,2,What will make you realize what the Nightcomer is
  86,3,"The star shining [before dawn]"
  86,4,"Each soul has a guardian [set up] over it"
  86,5,so let everyman notice what he has been created from
  86,6,He was created from a fluid ejected
  86,7,from between his backbone and his ribs
  86,8,He is Able to revive him
  86,9,on a day when secrets will be tested
  86,10,"so he will have no strength [left] nor any supporter"
  86,11,By the sky with its cycle
  86,12,by the earth cracking open
  86,13,it is a decisive statement
  86,14,It is no joke
  86,15,They are hatching some plot
  86,16,while I too am hatching a plot
  86,17,so put up with disbelievers; put up with them as long as you can